title: SPECIAL! Heat is Paid, Smoke Free, Walk to Dining, Endless Amenities!
posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Mike Miller | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', '2Br/2Ba - Outdoor Pool & Wetland Views!', 'W 78th St, Eden Prairie, MN', '$1840/mo', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage:', '1015 sqft.', 'Bedroom:', '2', 'Bathroom:', '2', 'Parking:', '2  Dedicated', 'Lease Duration:', '12 Months', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Pets Policy:', 'Cats & Dogs OK (75lb Max)', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Property Type:', 'Apartment', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Offering a remarkably unique community located in Eden Prairie within walking distance to restaurants and shopping.', 'Featuring 1, 1 plus den and 2 bedroom apartment homes with generous closet space, spacious kitchens, heated underground parking, outdoor pool, picnic areas, private party area, exercise room, library and community gardens.', 'Enjoy the amazing views of the protected wetland area located behind the community with plenty of space to get outside and enjoy the outdoors.', 'With nearby access to both Hwy 5', 'and Hwy 212 it will make it easy to get to a variety of nearby shopping and dining locations.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Pries and availability are subject to change.', 'Photos may not represent exact unit.', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'Washer/Dryer - Full Size Included', 'Elevator in Building', 'Controlled Building Access', 'On Bus Line', 'Car wash', 'Cable Ready', 'Trash chutes/recycling', 'BBQ Grilling Area', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Storage Available', 'Outdoor Pool', 'Heated Underground Parking', 'Pets Welcome!', 'Contact info:', 'Mike Miller', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info']
